                                                    Steelcase Reports First Quarter Results
                                                


                                                    GlobeNewswire – 
                                                    4:10 PM ET 06/21/2017
                                                


Steelcase Inc. (SCS) today reported first quarter revenue of $735.1 million and net income of $18.1 million, or diluted earnings of $0.15 per share. Revenue increased 2 percent, or approximately 4 percent on an organic basis, in the first quarter compared to the prior year, while orders increased 1 percent. Our first quarter results were consistent with our expectations.

















