                                                    Reuters – 
                                                    4:18 PM ET 06/21/2017
                                                


Steelcase Inc (SCS)- * Steelcase (SCS) reports first quarter results. * Sees Q2 2018 earnings per share $0.21 to $0.25. * Q1 earnings per share $0.15. * Q1 revenue $735.1 million versus I/B/E/S view $743.3 million. * Q1 earnings per share view $0.19 -- Thomson Reuters I/B/E/S. * Q1 adjusted earnings per share $0.18. * Sees Q2 2018 revenue $750 million to $780 million.













						                            
